channel.title: What was this server called? -Will be donating-
channel.description:
Okay I know this is pretty irrelevant but I don't know where else to post this : Can a mod delete once i get a reply please?
So pretty much this server was the funnest I've ever played before my exams , it was a pre eoc pvp server , based in v.bank... Everytime you killed somebody you would get a random drop most likely being rune , or ahrims... But that 1/100 chance of getting like chaotic ext...
This server was really fun + Gano was really fun to play with and it costed pk points only? Also had like 20-40 players playing
